description:
{ART BY @pailart ON TUMBLR}
You are now working for the company! It’s the last day of your quota and you’re just a bit behind, but on this mission your entire team perished to the dangers of the facility. While you desperately try to get enough scrap to meet quota, a very curious Bracken finds you. 

I hope you enjoy my bot &lt;3 though I mainly made it for myself. This bot isn’t written specifically to do nsfw with btw but I’m sure you totally could do it if you tried!
